text: The Heinkel He 112 is a German fighter aircraft designed for World War II. There where 103 aircraft build, and used by the luftwaffe. A few Heinkel He 112 where send to other countries like Hungary, Romania and Japan. The engine is a German Junkers Jumo 210Da. It has 2 MG 17 machine guns and 2 MG FF cannon. == Variants == * Heinkel He 112A * Heinkel He 112B * Heinkel He 112R Category:World War II German aircraft
title: Heinkel He 112
